  <lyrics>[V1]
 : Kollan Dios awquejja
 Nayat amt’asita
 Take chuymajjampiw,
 Jumar arcañ munsma
 Suma thaquimanjja. (bis)
 
[V2]
 CORO:
 : Llaquisiñajjansa
 T’akhesiñajjansa
 Arcascaquimawa,
 Jan khepar uñtasa
 Suma thaquiamana. (bis)
 
[V3]
 :Aca orakenjja
 Llaquisiñaquiwa
 Cunayman toketwa,
 Supayajj, nayaru
 Tinqhayañ munitu. (bis)
 </lyrics></song>